      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 20:53:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞分析师称谷歌需要走出去并花钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/google-needs-to-go-out-and-spend-says-jefferies-analyst-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Jefferies 分析师 Brent Thill 表示，现在是投资的好时机，因为尽管谷歌的云计算增长令人失望，但今年的资本支出仍高达 750 亿美元。他与 Caroline Hyde 和 Jackie Davalos 一起在“彭博科技”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/google-needs-to-go-out-and-spend-says-jefferies-analyst-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 20:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储古尔斯比警告关税将影响通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-goolsbee-warns-about-inflation-impact-of-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比警告称，持续的关税可能导致供应链再次中断并推高通胀。他在底特律芝加哥联邦储备银行的汽车会议上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-goolsbee-warns-about-inflation-impact-of-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 20:37:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
