    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风波中黄金交易商以折扣价抛售英国央行黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-dealers-sell-boe-bullion-at-big-discounts-in-tariff-panic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对特朗普潜在关税的担忧引发了对金条的争夺，导致人们排队数周才能提取黄金，英格兰银行金库中的黄金交易价格低于大盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-dealers-sell-boe-bullion-at-big-discounts-in-tariff-panic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商撤离 油价跌至 2025 年以来最低结算价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统就职后的几周内，由于交易员不断退出市场，油价跌至今年最低收盘价。]]></description>
